---
---
<section class="roadmap" id="roadmap">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="text-gradient">Swamp Domination Roadmap</h2>
      <p>Strategic, unstoppable, and ready to conquer the next swamp.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item active">
        <div class="phase-badge">Phase 01</div>
        <h3>SWAMP</h3>
        <p>Token launch, genesis airdrop to early swamp-dwellers, liquidity ignition, and the first layering event.</p>
        <span class="status pulse">IN PROGRESS</span>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="phase-badge">Phase 02</div>
        <h3>ONION</h3>
        <p>Cross-exchange listings, Donkey-approved integrations, and Shrek lore-driven NFT ascent.</p>
        <span class="status">UPCOMING</span>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="phase-badge">Phase 03</div>
        <h3>OGRE</h3>
        <p>DAO governance, recurring layering events, and global swamp raids to expand the territory.</p>
        <span class="status">UPCOMING</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-banner glass-card">
      <h2>EMPOWER THE SWAMP</h2>
      <p>Every token holder is part of an elite squad of swamp-dwellers. Join the mission to transform early believers into the next wave of crypto millionaires.</p>
      <div class="cta-btns">
        <a href="#buy" class="btn btn-primary">GET $SHREK NOW</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline">VIEW ONIONPAPER</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .roadmap {
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .timeline {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    background: var(--glass);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-item.active {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 77, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .phase-badge {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .timeline-item p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .status {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .status.pulse {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: white;
    animation: soft-pulse 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes soft-pulse {
    0% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.7; }
    100% { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .cta-banner {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(164, 198, 57, 0.1), transparent), var(--glass);
  }

  .cta-banner h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-banner p {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .cta-btns {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .timeline { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cta-btns { flex-direction: column; }
  }
</style>
